<L>__{ext interior a beacon hill house night}
<A>__{the robbery, in quick cuts: a door lock is picked by sophia. pencil flashlight passes an upstairs window. rudy in the car. silver removed from a drawer by shorty. peg walking down the street, as lookout. malcolm takes off his shoes. the sleeping old man, old talcum powder, as malcolm takes a watch, a wallet from within inches of his pillow. then, more boldly, picks up the man's hand and removes a ring from one of his fingers. shorty watching with bated breath, he's about to have a heart attack.}
